  "pink-riad-tulum-moroccan-inspired-luxury-residences": "<p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\">Welcome to Pink Riad Tulum \u2013 Moroccan-Inspired Luxury Residences</p>\r\nPink Riad is an exclusive residential development in Tulum, blending the elegance of Moroccan architecture with the tropical beauty of the Riviera Maya. Nestled in the prestigious Aldea Zama, just minutes from Tulum\u2019s beaches and hotel zone, Pink Riad offers a unique lifestyle infused with Moorish charm and modern comfort.\r\n\r\nPrime Location in Tulum: Located in the heart of Aldea Zama, Pink Riad is only 5 minutes from the beach, the vibrant hotel zone, and downtown Tulum. This master-planned community provides convenience while offering privacy and tranquility.\r\n\r\nElegant Moroccan-Style Residences: Pink Riad features exquisitely designed housing units integrated into a 3-story Riad-style building, inspired by the rich culture and aesthetics of Marrakech. The development showcases handmade terracotta tiles, arabesque wood carvings, and timeless decor elements.\r\n\r\nProperty Options:\r\n<ul data-spread=\"false\">\r\n \t<li>Ground Houses: Spacious homes with terraces, swim-up pools, and green areas. Sizes range from 100.53 m\u00b2 to 153.06 m\u00b2.</li>\r\n \t<li>Terrace Houses: Stylish apartments featuring private terraces. Sizes range from 88.80 m\u00b2 to 92.68 m\u00b2.</li>\r\n \t<li>Penthouses with Rooftops: Luxurious two-level residences with private rooftop terraces, bars, and jacuzzis. Sizes range from 168.15 m\u00b2 to 170.69 m\u00b2.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nExclusive Amenities:\r\n<ul data-spread=\"false\">\r\n \t<li>Concierge Service</li>\r\n \t<li>24/7 Security &amp; Front Desk</li>\r\n \t<li>Wellness Center</li>\r\n \t<li>Riad-Style Pool</li>\r\n \t<li>Masterplanned Community</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAuthentic Design &amp; Premium Finishes: Each residence is crafted with regional materials, including terracotta, polished finishes, and intricate Moroccan details, offering warmth and sophistication.\r\n\r\nWhy Choose Pink Riad Tulum?\r\n<ul data-spread=\"false\">\r\n \t<li>Prime location near Tulum Beach and Aldea Zama</li>\r\n \t<li>Unique Moroccan-inspired architecture</li>\r\n \t<li>Private pools, terraces, and rooftop jacuzzis</li>\r\n \t<li>Exclusive amenities for privacy and comfort</li>\r\n \t<li>Investment opportunity in one of Tulum\u2019s top developments</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nInvest in Your Dream Home: Pink Riad Tulum offers a rare blend of cultural elegance and modern convenience, perfect for personal living or as a high-value vacation rental.\r\n\r\nSecure Your Unit in Pink Riad Tulum Today.",
  "oniric-tulum-surreal-luxury-residences-in-the-heart-of-nature": "Welcome to Oniric Tulum \u2013 Surreal Luxury Residences in the Heart of Nature\r\n\r\nOniric Tulum is an exclusive low-density residential development inspired by dreams and surrealist art. Nestled in Region 8, Tulum\u2019s most coveted area, just 5 minutes from the beach and 7 minutes from downtown, Oniric offers a fusion of architectural creativity, privacy, and nature-inspired luxury.\r\n\r\n<strong>Prime Location:</strong>\r\nLocated in Region 8, the closest area to Tulum\u2019s pristine beaches, Oniric is a high-potential investment hub with easy access via Guardianes Mayas Ave. and 65th Ave., only 500 meters from Kukulkan Avenue leading directly to the coast.\r\n\r\n<strong>Unique Residences:</strong>\r\nOniric features 27 exclusive condos with 1, 2, and 3-bedroom layouts. Each unit is designed for maximum privacy, with no cross views, private pools, and either a rooftop terrace or garden.\r\n\r\n<strong>Signature Design &amp; Architecture:</strong>\r\nInspired by surrealism, cenotes, and nature\u2019s fractal geometry, Oniric\u2019s architecture fosters creativity. Its iconic central flower-shaped cenote pool and floating staircases create a dreamlike atmosphere, emphasizing light, shadow, and fluidity throughout the spaces.\r\n\r\n<strong>World-Class Amenities:</strong>\r\n\r\nOniric Cenote Pool\r\n\r\nRooftop Infinity Pool\r\n\r\nHanging Gardens\r\n\r\nReflecting Pool\r\n\r\nSpeakeasy with Gourmet Dining &amp; Wine Cellar\r\n\r\nYoga &amp; Meditation Area\r\n\r\nMassage Area &amp; Temazcal\r\n\r\nIce Bath\r\n\r\nCoworking Space\r\n\r\nWellness Center (Detox Area)\r\n\r\nGourmet Kitchen (Retox Area)\r\n\r\nLobby, Security, Elevator &amp; Parking\r\n\r\n<strong>Nature Integration &amp; Sustainability:</strong>\r\nOniric seamlessly blends with Tulum\u2019s natural environment, utilizing non-linear patterns, water elements, and eco-friendly design principles, ensuring harmony between architecture and nature.\r\n\r\nWhy Invest in Oniric Tulum?\r\n\r\nRegion 8\u2019s prime location with high capital gains potential\r\n\r\nExclusive low-density development (27 units)\r\n\r\nPrivate pools, rooftop terraces, and gardens\r\n\r\nUnique surrealist-inspired architecture\r\n\r\nResort-style amenities tailored for wellness and creativity\r\n\r\nInvest in Your Dream Lifestyle:\r\nOniric Tulum is more than a residence\u2014it\u2019s a gateway to a surreal world of creativity, wellness, and luxury. Ideal for personal living or as a high-return vacation rental.\r\n\r\nSecure Your Condo in Oniric Tulum Today.",
